            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>DA is Moz’s metric and blends over 40 signals including link quality and diversity. DR is Ahrefs’ metric focused on the strength of the referring-domain graph. Both are 1–100 logarithmic scales; use whichever your team standardizes on.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

